    "patch_code": "static boolean mayBeString(Node n, boolean recurse) {\n   if (recurse) {\n     return allResultsMatch(n, MAY_BE_STRING_PREDICATE);\n   } else {\n     return n instanceof Literal && ((Literal) n).isString();\n   }\n }",
